===The Beauty===
Explorers set up parasols and beach chairs at some places in the area due to the stunning view. They mentioned that "I enjoyed being here, chilling." For explorers, this is a good place to rest and stay.
Below is a memo by one of the explorers:

''We found a good place to stay! Parasols, beach chairs, and food! We had a good dinner here and sang and danced.'' 

''We three people enjoyed the endless sunset here. The pink sky is soft, stunning, and bright. I really love it. My dream is to swim in the pool!''

{{Blurimage|file=vaca.png|caption=Parasols in Level 413 by explorers. Took by James Soana.|align=center}}

''-James Soana''
