<div class="title">
==Entities==
</div>
There are entities recorded at this level. For example, a dark object that is reported to be walking on the liquid. No information is available currently since no explorers who left the level have seen any entities. The only image available is believed to be attacked near the entrance of level 413 from [[level 0]].

{{Blurimage|file=IDK Image.png|caption=Unknown situation, believed to be attacked by <ruby>entities<rp>(</rp><rt>the dark thing</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby>. Photographer <ruby>missing<rp>(</rp><rt>dead</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby>. Walls with pattern of Level 0 is found.|align=center}}

===Entity 1: The Dark===


An entity with dark body was recorded by a cameraman exploring the level on 15th June, 2016. He sent us a message with a photo showing a small and blurry dark dot floating on the carbo-liquid surface, with a short message "''Hope I am not <ruby>its<rp>(</rp><rt>the Dark</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby> target.''". The cameraman is currently missing. The entity is given the name "The Dark". Scientisits observed the information available and believed that The Dark absorbs energy to expand itself from the carbo-liquid and turns offensive once a certain size is reached.

{{Underline}}
<div class="title">
==Colonies and Outposts==
</div>
No colonies are set up in this level, according to record.

However, it is rumored that an outpost is set up at E-34 district in the level. Its existence has not yet been proved.

Due to the level's special properties and unexpected behaviors, setting up colonies or outposts is extremely difficult. 

{{Underline}}
<div class="title">
==Entrances and Exits==
</div>This is a perfect place for <ruby>vacation<rp>(</rp><rt>relax & immerse</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby>, but never stay too long.

===Entrances ===      
*Walls with yellow patterns of Level 0 is found in this level. It is believed that an entrance is available in [[Level 0]].
* Sinking into the bottom of the deepest pool in [[Level 37]] will have small chance of being teleported to a dark area in Level 413.
*[[Level 8]] is also considered one of the entrances of Level 413.
*One might be transferred to Level 413 under very rare situations from [[Level 13]].

{{Blurimage|file=Hallway413.png|caption=The "Hallway"|align=center}}
=== Exits ===  
*Reaching the end of the <ruby>"sea"<rp>(</rp><rt>path towards death</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby> and find <ruby>land<rp>(</rp><rt>no such heaven</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby>. Find a cave on natural land can lead one to a random location in [[Level 42]].
*Walking through the only <ruby>straight hallway<rp>(</rp><rt>it is the exclamation!</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby> "The Hallway" to reach a <ruby>random level<rp>(</rp><rt>it isn't!</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby>. But please always pay attention to your back, as entities from other levels are often teleported to The Hallway due to its unstable structure.
* A golden metal door with renaissance patterns can lead one to [[Level 30]].




